               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Maṣḥafa ʾaślǝṭi, Lectionary for the entire year (fols. 1ra-72ra)
                     I-1) Scriptural readings for liturgical periods, fasts and feasts (for the
                     entire year) (fols. 1ra-69rb)
 I-2) Lectionary for feasts (fols.
                     69rb-72ra)
 
 Additiones 1-4.</summary>
